dct_title_s: Middle Township, New Jersey tax map
dct_description_sm: This is a collection of maps of Middle Township that are to be used along with the Environmental Resource Inventory of Middle. The maps focus upon zoning, open space & government owned parcels, center designations, and taxes.
Prepared for the Township of Middle with a grant from the Department of Environmental Protection, Office of Environmental Services.
One of four maps belonging to the Environmental Resource Inventory: Middle Township (Phase II).
